title: Aml Pages TwinkiePaste v2.16.436
description:
Aml Pages TwinkiePaste v2.16.436

TwinkiePaste is the utility to quickly typing commonly used text, dates, greetings, standard responses, Internet URLs, logins and passwords, code templates. TwinkiePaste helps to quickly type text in almost any application, thus saving a lot of time and saving you from routine.

Features

Pastes plain or formatted text into any applications
Keeps the clipboard history
Smart text insertion using macros: selected text, datetime, usernames and etc.
Configurable hotkeys
Simple, lightweight and user friendly phrase editor
Unicode support. Minimal system requirements
No proprietary file format. Our database is simple XML only
Check for updates: automatically every 1-2-3...X day or manually from menu
Also we can suggest portable version
Multilingual user interface include English, French, Hungarian, Italian, Polish, Russian, Spanish, Turkish, Ukrainian and other. Translate the user interface and get it free.

Official Website: http://amlpages.com/twinkiepaste.shtml
